isang spark sa lugar ng trabaho—

579
00:30:23,790 --> 00:30:24,990
hindi kayo manloloko.

580
00:30:25,310 --> 00:30:26,710
Partners in arms kayo,

581
00:30:27,160 --> 00:30:27,820
