595
00:30:59,900 --> 00:31:01,700
Dahil wala pa akong career.

596
00:31:02,600 --> 00:31:04,810
Ang mga babaeng may karera ay hindi espesyal.

597
00:31:04,940 --> 00:31:06,660
Trabaho lang yan.

598
00:31:07,380 --> 00:31:09,030
Isipin mo ang iyong sarili noon.

599
00:31:09,030 --> 00:31:09,790
Sumuko ka

600
