614
00:31:46,510 --> 00:31:47,510
Kaya ito ay sa kanya.

615
00:31:55,970 --> 00:31:56,900
ayos lang. inaamin ko.

616
00:31:57,210 --> 00:31:58,610
Dumating nga siya para makita ako.

617
00:31:58,630 --> 00:31:59,900
Pero pinalayas ko siya.

618
00:31:59,960 --> 00:32:00,510
Hindi ko akalain

619
00:32:00,510 --> 00:32:02,440
gagawa siya ng dirty trick na ganyan.

620
00:32:02,590 --> 00:32:03,240
Hindi ko akalain...

621
00:32:03,240 --> 00:32:05,500
Kaya bago ako makarating sa Svelto Hotel Group—

622
00:32:05,550 --> 00:32:07,270
