627
00:32:16,580 --> 00:32:17,940
Nagpalit ka ba ng kwarto?

628
00:32:19,620 --> 00:32:20,250
Ginang Nie.

629
00:32:20,680 --> 00:32:22,590
Si Mr. Nie ay isang VIP guest sa aming hotel.

630
00:32:22,590 --> 00:32:24,350
Kaka-upgrade lang namin ng kwarto niya

631
00:32:24,370 --> 00:32:25,400
