680
00:34:13,100 --> 00:34:14,750
[Yuhua Hotel Co., Ltd.
Pahayag ng Account]

681
00:34:17,920 --> 00:34:19,000
Hanapin mo si Feng Bin.

682
00:34:19,550 --> 00:34:20,810
Siya ang may hawak nito.

683
00:34:21,440 --> 00:34:23,810
Pinipigilan kami ni Feng Bin
