709
00:35:39,680 --> 00:35:40,890
[Lagda ng Customer: Nie Yucheng]

710
00:35:42,190 --> 00:35:43,650
Pumunta kausapin ang accountant.

711
00:35:51,550 --> 00:35:52,480
Anong ibig mong sabihin?

712
00:35:52,710 --> 00:35:54,280
Alam mong hindi yun ang gusto ko.

713
00:35:54,280 --> 00:35:55,480
Nasa kritikal na yugto ka sa iyong karera.

714
00:35:55,480 --> 00:35:56,480
Ang pagkakaroon ng isang sanggol

715
00:35:56,480 --> 00:35:57,800
