At wala akong ideya

734
00:36:50,470 --> 00:36:51,630
ano ang gagawin ngayon.

735
00:36:56,670 --> 00:36:58,590
Huwag palaging isipin na ang damo ay mas luntian
sa kabila.

736
00:36:58,590 --> 00:37:00,190
Akalain mong lumayo dito

737
00:37:00,190 --> 00:37:01,920
ay hahantong sa isang bagay na mas mahusay?

738
00:37:02,100 --> 00:37:03,830
Parang naghihintay ng bus.

739
00:37:03,850 --> 00:37:05,510
Maghihintay ka magpakailanman, at hindi ito darating.

740
00:37:05,510 --> 00:37:07,040
Kaya nagpasya kang sumakay ng taxi.

741
00:37:07,440 --> 00:37:09,110
Ngunit hindi ka makakakuha ng isa
at mapupunta ka ulit sa pila.

742
00:37:09,110 --> 00:37:10,110
Tapos tumalikod ka

743
00:37:10,110 --> 00:37:12,000
at nakaalis na ang bus.

744
00:37:12,000 --> 00:37:14,260
At bumalik ka kung saan ka nagsimula.

745
00:37:25,320 --> 00:37:28,380
Bakit biglang meron
isang daang taong paglalakad na kaganapan?

746
00:37:28,800 --> 00:37:29,920
Sinabi ko sa iyo na makipag-ugnayan kay Director Zhang

747
00:37:29,920 --> 00:37:30,670
at ayusin ito!

748
00:37:30,670 --> 00:37:32,280
Tinawagan mo ba siya o hindi?

749
00:37:34,960 --> 00:37:37,960
Pagtawag sa Sports Bureau chief
ay walang silbi ngayon.

750
00:37:38,320 --> 00:37:40,720
Maaari mo bang subukan ang opisyal ng lokal na pamahalaan?

751
00:37:40,920 --> 00:37:41,840
Tama na! Cut the crap!

752
00:37:41,840 --> 00:37:43,170
Gawin mo lang ang sinasabi ko, okay?

753
00:38:02,180 --> 00:38:03,640
Uminom ka muna ng gamot mo.

754
00:38:04,380 --> 00:38:06,710
May nakahandang lugaw na dawa sa kaldero.

755
00:38:08,540 --> 00:38:09,800
Pwede mo ba akong dalhan ng mangkok?

756
00:38:11,960 --> 00:38:12,670
honey.

757
00:38:23,000 --> 00:38:24,880
Hiniling ko sa iyo na kausapin ang opisyal.

758
00:38:24,880 --> 00:38:26,340
Nakalusot ka ba o hindi?

759
00:38:27,280 --> 00:38:28,280
Anong ibig mong sabihin?

760
00:38:43,220 --> 00:38:44,220
Halika humiga ka.

761
00:38:49,110 --> 00:38:50,570
Uminom ka muna ng gamot mo.

762
00:39:08,800 --> 00:39:09,470
Dito.

763
00:39:29,840 --> 00:39:30,550
Miyu.

764
00:39:31,890 --> 00:39:33,170
Pagod na pagod na ako.

765
00:39:34,370 --> 00:39:35,370
Iniisip ko...

766
00:39:37,280 --> 00:39:38,680
kung hindi ko ginawa

767
00:39:38,700 --> 00:39:40,050
kailangang magtrabaho,

768
00:39:40,670 --> 00:39:42,600
Kaya kong manatili sa tabi mo araw-araw.

769
00:39:43,520 --> 00:39:44,770
Kahit walang ginagawa,

770
00:39:45,700 --> 00:39:47,260
nakahiga lang dito sa tabi mo—

771
00:39:48,280 --> 00:39:49,940
Ako ang magiging pinakamasayang tao sa buhay.

772
00:40:00,150 --> 00:40:00,920
Miyu.

773
00:40:01,840 --> 00:40:03,900
Alagaan mo lang ako ng ganito,

774
00:40:04,920 --> 00:40:06,180
sa buong buhay ko,

775
00:40:07,320 --> 00:40:08,190
gagawin mo?

776
00:40:10,730 --> 00:40:11,690
Tumigil ka sa pagsasalita.

777
00:40:17,380 --> 00:40:18,270
Alam ko

778
00:40:19,190 --> 00:40:20,450
galit ka pa rin sa akin,

779
00:40:21,320 --> 00:40:22,110
tama ba?

780
00:40:30,560 --> 00:40:32,460
Alam kong maraming nangyari lately.

781
00:40:33,530 --> 00:40:35,660
Ginawa ka nito

782
00:40:36,070 --> 00:40:37,270
nag-aalala at nababalisa.

783
00:40:37,270 --> 00:40:38,230
pasensya na po.

784
00:40:39,070 --> 00:40:40,280
Kasalanan ko to.

785
00:40:40,880 --> 00:40:42,810
Hindi sapat na seguridad ang ibinigay ko sa iyo.

786
00:40:43,280 --> 00:40:45,280
Pero hindi ko talaga kayang mabuhay ng wala ka.

787
00:40:45,460 --> 00:40:46,120
Miyu.

788
00:40:46,760 --> 00:40:48,160
Isipin mo na lang ito—

789
00:40:48,280 --> 00:40:49,710
nakadikit ka sa akin,

790
00:40:51,800 --> 00:40:53,280
at hinding hindi kita bibitawan.

791
00:40:55,710 --> 00:40:56,770
Paano naman ako?

792
00:41:00,090 --> 00:41:01,490
Saan ako iiwan nito?

793
00:41:06,320 --> 00:41:07,780
Lagi kang nasa puso ko.

794
00:41:08,800 --> 00:41:09,840
Ako, Nie Yucheng,

795
00:41:10,280 --> 00:41:11,760
nagsumikap sa lahat ng mga taon na ito

796
00:41:11,760 --> 00:41:13,070
sa isang dahilan lang—

797
00:41:15,310 --> 00:41:16,100
ikaw.

798
00:41:22,630 --> 00:41:23,800
Mula ngayon,

799
00:41:24,690 --> 00:41:26,600
Hindi ko hahayaang masaktan ka.

800
00:41:27,280 --> 00:41:28,800
Poprotektahan kita magpakailanman,

801
00:41:30,000 --> 00:41:31,800
at protektahan ang aming pamilya magpakailanman.

802
00:41:32,550 --> 00:41:33,400
I swear.

803
00:41:34,310 --> 00:41:35,430
Magtitiwala ka ba sa akin?

804
00:41:45,750 --> 00:41:47,560
♪ Isang kurap ng madilim na liwanag ♪

805
00:41:49,460 --> 00:41:51,340
♪ Isang mangkok ng mainit na sopas ♪

806
00:41:52,830 --> 00:41:54,770
♪ Mga tao sa lungsod ♪

807
00:41:55,540 --> 00:41:58,580
♪ Pumipisil sa pagmamadali ♪

808
00:42:00,410 --> 00:42:02,030
♪ Ang mga palad ng oras ♪

809
00:42:04,130 --> 00:42:07,200
♪ Paggiling sa mga simpleng araw ♪

810
00:42:07,890 --> 00:42:10,810
♪ Pagwiwisik sa kanila sa abalang mundong ito ♪

811
00:42:11,850 --> 00:42:14,080
♪ Para matikman, unti-unti ♪

812
00:42:15,410 --> 00:42:18,440
♪ Pagyakap sa nagniningning na mundong ito ♪

813
00:42:19,120 --> 00:42:22,150
♪ Pinipigilan ang puso mula sa pagkupas hanggang kulay abo ♪

814
00:42:22,740 --> 00:42:25,860
♪ Ang saya, kalungkutan, lamig, at init ng buhay ♪

815
00:42:26,600 --> 00:42:29,080
♪ Intertwined sa loob ng makamundong ♪

816
00:42:28,280 --> 00:42:29,190
Sabi ng ilang tao

817
00:42:29,400 --> 00:42:31,400
kasinungalingan ang nagpapaganda ng buhay.

818
00:42:30,730 --> 00:42:33,880
♪ Magtipon tayo nang buong tapang ♪

819
00:42:31,960 --> 00:42:32,800
Para silang candy

820
00:42:32,800 --> 00:42:35,070
nakabalot sa makulay na cellophane.

821
00:42:34,500 --> 00:42:37,870
♪ Ang kinalimutang nakaraan ♪

822
00:42:35,590 --> 00:42:37,800
Hinayaan ka nilang mamuhay sa maling tamis,

823
00:42:37,840 --> 00:42:40,110
para hindi mo na kailangang harapin
ang mapait na katotohanan.

824
00:42:38,850 --> 00:42:41,120
♪ Maaaring may pagsisisi ♪

825
00:42:41,360 --> 00:42:43,760
Alam kong nagsisinungaling ako sa sarili ko.

826
00:42:42,780 --> 00:42:45,020
♪ Maaaring may kalungkutan ♪

827
00:42:44,150 --> 00:42:45,800
Pero minsan,

828
00:42:45,800 --> 00:42:47,480
nabubuhay sa mundo ng kasinungalingan

829
00:42:46,030 --> 00:42:49,330
♪ Pagyakap sa nagniningning na mundong ito ♪

830
00:42:47,920 --> 00:42:50,230
ay ang tanging paraan upang makaramdam ng kasiyahan.

831
00:42:49,760 --> 00:42:52,760
♪ Pinipigilan ang puso mula sa pagkupas hanggang kulay abo ♪

832
00:42:53,690 --> 00:42:56,680
♪ Ang saya, kalungkutan, lamig, at init ng buhay ♪

833
00:42:57,440 --> 00:42:59,820
♪ Intertwined sa loob ng makamundong ♪

834
00:43:00,810 --> 00:43:04,130
♪ Magtipon tayo nang buong tapang ♪

835
00:43:04,840 --> 00:43:08,000
♪ Ang kinalimutang nakaraan ♪

836
00:43:10,350 --> 00:43:12,650
♪ Naglalakad sa mundong ito ♪

837
00:43:13,720 --> 00:43:16,530
♪ Walang pinagsisisihan ♪

